            "created_at": "2017-04-04T18:41:31Z",
            "updated_at": "2017-04-04T18:41:31Z",
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I agree, it should not be a requirement to modify sys.path or any environment variables to access the cli via the flask command.  It should also not be a requirement that your flask app is installed with setuptools for this to work in a nice way.\r\n\r\nIf nobody is working on this, I would be interested in investigating writing a patch for it."
